          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm leading-[1.6] m-0">A full-stack campaign site built with Rails 8. Featuring SEO/AEO optimization, dynamic content management, and a bold visual identity. Enough is Enough.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <a href="https://rml-clough-97072a2e05ec.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank" class="rounded-lg py-2 px-4 bg-orange-600 cursor-pointer hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors">
              <span class="uppercase text-zinc-950 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold text-xs">View Live</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# Italian Garden %>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 h-48 lg:h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-zinc-600 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] text-xl uppercase">Italian Garden</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-[13px]">RESTAURANT</span>
          <h3 class="text-zinc-50 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold text-2xl uppercase m-0">Italian Garden Restaurant</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm leading-[1.6] m-0">A warm, inviting restaurant site with online menu, photo gallery, reviews, and Google Maps integration. Built to bring in diners who are searching for a great meal.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-lg py-2 px-4 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-xs">Coming Soon</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%# El Mexicano %>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-12 rounded-xl bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 h-48 lg:h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-zinc-600 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] text-xl uppercase">El Mexicano</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col gap-4">
          <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-[13px]">RESTAURANT</span>
          <h3 class="text-zinc-50 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold text-2xl uppercase m-0">El Mexicano</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm leading-[1.6] m-0">Authentic Mexican restaurant site with admin dashboard, menu management, and a bold visual identity. Custom-built with Rails 8 and Tailwind CSS.</p>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="rounded-lg py-2 px-4 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-500 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-xs">Coming Soon</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%# ─── ABOUT ─── %>
  <section class="flex flex-col items-center w-full py-16 md:py-24 gap-8 md:gap-12 px-6 md:px-16 border-t border-zinc-800">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8 lg:gap-16 w-full max-w-200">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-2/5 flex justify-center">
        <div class="w-48 h-48 md:w-64 md:h-64 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <%= image_tag "mason_roberts_3.png", alt: "Mason Roberts", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full lg:w-3/5 flex flex-col gap-5">
        <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-[13px]">THE DEVELOPER</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-[0.02em] text-zinc-50 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold m-0">Mason Roberts</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-base leading-[1.7] m-0">I'm an auto technician by trade and a developer by passion. I spent years turning wrenches in Rock Hill before I started building web applications. I know what it's like to run a small business — the long hours, the tight budgets, the pride in doing honest work.</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-base leading-[1.7] m-0">That's why I build websites differently. No cookie-cutter templates. No confusing contracts. No disappearing after launch. I build sites the way I'd want someone to fix my truck — with care, transparency, and the kind of craftsmanship you can see.</p>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-base leading-[1.7] m-0">Rogue Media Lab is my studio. Every project is built with Ruby on Rails, hosted on enterprise-grade infrastructure, and maintained so you never have to worry about it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%# ─── CONTACT ─── %>
  <section id="contact" class="flex flex-col items-center w-full py-16 md:py-24 gap-12 md:gap-16 px-6 md:px-16 border-t border-zinc-800">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-3 max-w-200">
      <span class="text-orange-500 font-mono text-[13px]">GET IN TOUCH</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-[0.02em] uppercase text-center text-zinc-50 font-['Barlow_Condensed',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold m-0">Start Your Project</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[18px] leading-[1.6] text-center text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] max-w-162 m-0">Tell me about your business and what you need. I'll get back to you within 24 hours.</p>
    </div>

    <div id="contact_form" class="w-full max-w-lg">
      <%= form_with model: @contact, url: contacts_path, class: "flex flex-col gap-5" do |form| %>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <%= form.label :f_name, "First Name", class: "text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm" %>
            <%= form.text_field :f_name, class: "w-full rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-50 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none transition-colors", placeholder: "John" %>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <%= form.label :l_name, "Last Name", class: "text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm" %>
            <%= form.text_field :l_name, class: "w-full rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-50 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none transition-colors", placeholder: "Smith" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <%= form.label :email, "Email", class: "text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm" %>
            <%= form.email_field :email, class: "w-full rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-50 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none transition-colors", placeholder: "john@example.com" %>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <%= form.label :phone, "Phone", class: "text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm" %>
            <%= form.telephone_field :phone, class: "w-full rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-50 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none transition-colors", placeholder: "(803) 555-1234" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
          <%= form.label :description, "Tell us about your project", class: "text-zinc-400 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm" %>
          <%= form.text_area :description, rows: 5, class: "w-full rounded-lg bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-zinc-50 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] text-sm px-4 py-3 focus:border-orange-500 focus:outline-none transition-colors resize-none", placeholder: "What does your business do? What kind of site are you looking for?" %>
        </div>
        <div>
          <%= form.submit "Send Message", class: "w-full rounded-lg py-3 px-6 bg-orange-600 cursor-pointer hover:bg-orange-500 transition-colors text-zinc-950 font-['Inter',system-ui,sans-serif] font-bold text-sm uppercase" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%= render "shared/workbench_footer", section_name: "The Lab" %>

</div>
